description:
Just a simple theme designed for TinyChan to replace the original colours.

Edit 13/07/09:
You may want to add this to the script for a banner which fits in with the color scheme.
	/* Logo fix */
	body img[src$="banner.png"] {
	height: 31px !important;
	width: 0px !important;
	padding-left: 148px !important;
	background-image: url("http://bayimg.com/image/bacgaaacg.jpg") !important;}

css:
@namespace url(http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml);

@-moz-document domain("www.tinychan.org") {
	body{background-color:#DFF8FF !IMPORTANT;}
	a{color:#000000 !IMPORTANT;}
	.d, .c, .l , .post, .head{padding:4px 0 !IMPORTANT; background-color:#6FDBDB !IMPORTANT;}
	.c{background-color:#FFFFFF !IMPORTANT; border-top:solid 2px #33CCCC !IMPORTANT;}
	.l{background-color:#33CCCC !IMPORTANT;}
	.l:hover, .d:hover{background-color:#FF9900 !IMPORTANT;}
	.head{background-color:#6FDBDB !IMPORTANT;}
	.post{background-color:#FFFFFF !IMPORTANT;}
	/* Made by Harry Wright */

}
